data.name: TBHELP.Text
data.value:
Basics: To get started keep pressing the banana button until you reach the required amount to by the wooden hands. When you reach 50 Wooden Hands the Stone hands get unlocked. The same goes on for the other hands, reach 50 then a new hand unlocks. BPC = Bananas Per Click BPS = Bananas Per Second
Monki Hands: The Monki Hands shop currently has 12 hands, Starting with the wooden hands and ending with the Blackstone Hands. Each Hand gets more expensive thus giving it a better BPC Amount. When you reach a certain amount of specific hand you get a small multiplier applied to it.
Monki Shop: The Monki Shop Gets Unlocked at 50 Stone Hands. The Monki Shop Allows you to hire monkis so that you don't need to click. They give you Idle cash which is called BPS. The Monki Shop starts on a Monki called Marmocets and ends with Homo Sapiens. The Price and BPS increase the more monkis you unlock!
Upgrades: Once you've reached 50 Orangutans you unlock a tab called upgrades which allows you to spend Bananas on small upgrades to each of your Monki Hands and Monkis, which lets you progress more into the game. The pricing is Base 10.
Prestige:
Once you have reached 250 Homo Sapiens and have reached Duodecillion, you unlock prestiging. Prestiging resets all your data, However it gives you intelligence which gives the Monki Hands and Monki Shops an upgrade, this can boost you and how much money you make. The more you prestige the more of a multiplier you get which allows you to get more banananas which allow you to grow you Kongolian Empire!
Breaking the Universe:
Once you've reached 1 Centillion Or 1e303, you've pretty much finished the game. currently you will be locked out of the Main game when you have reached 1 centillion. reaching centillon takes a long time. So have fun. :D

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
When you reach past 1 Duodecillion (DD) You get One Intelligence (📓 for every Duodecillion. Saving up the Intelligence (📓) will give you a small multiplier at first, but will progressivly increase. You can spend Intelligence on Permanant upgrades which makes your game move faster.
However all your progress will be deleted!
